 Blessing Uzzi’s short film “Sister Rose” has officially premiered on YouTube. “Sister Rose” stars Uzoamaka Aniunoh, Daniel Seaman, ex-BBNaija housemate Neo Akpofure and is directed by Blessing Uzzi. Explaining how love can leave us on the day we need it the most, the short film follows the story of a young lady who quit the convent to surprise the love of her life and experience the love of Valentine but gets surprised instead as he decides to become a reverend father. Watch the short film below: 